{"tid":1802136,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和你shop 問題討論","createTime":"2019-12-29T08:16:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T08:50:15.000Z","uid":341788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7970ebabb06fb294f44473368c26aa368cb9654c","tid":1802136,"uid":341788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:16:45.000Z","msg":"大家而家成日講和你shop都有好大風險<br />\n小弟有幾個idea同大家分享吓（水貨客地區更適用）<br />\n其實之前都有巴絲提過 不過好似冇乜人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.裝扮問題<br />\nblack block只適用於裝修工人 若果大家唔諗住做就着返行街look融入人群 令班畜牲分唔到你係示威者定遊客<br />\n<br />\n2.道具<br />\n可以用浮誇啲既道具裝扮自己成大媽或者係成身supreme既大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於和你shop既原意係為左阻礙商場業務 所以大家千其唔好帶埋gip去shopping 搞到1個人霸幾個人既位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（後生既就盡量唔好帶喇 因為太顯眼了）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.語言<br />\n首選當然係同袍們既普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其次英文或各國語言 再者就係香港話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.任務<br />\n盡量以人數逼爆商場啲藍店 一抽二袋少不免 加埋gipgip更貼心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有大家可以喺店舖入面適當地同朋友鬧下交增進感情 令店舖更熱鬧<br />\n 個人建議大家盡量唔好嗌口號 因為我哋真係黎買野架 只不過揀耐少少炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n關於一啲鐘意踢gip或者同水貨客友善交流既手足我個人係十分g持的 但係由於而家啲卧低狗狗太多了 希望大家小心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家覺得有用就推推la <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc2da04ab7ec9c58d978dc8cb869f76d408b363c","tid":1802136,"uid":341788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:20:15.000Z","msg":"push 1"},{"pid":"479f40c19604526ac106fd360eca12f7cf3873e7","tid":1802136,"uid":158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:50:15.000Z","msg":"大家幫手宣傳下，ig,fb,tg,Twitter 同你身邊既朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sa5sWmr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSa5sWmr.jpg&h=2e6a418c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2skMss7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2skMss7.jpg&h=077c238a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[召喚] 簽名師唔該全面進場 (你地自己睇下羞唔羞恥) (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801519\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801519</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n最新日程表出咗啦 除夕元旦都有行動呀<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/1798785\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1798785</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}